    <briefdescription>
<para>The native base class for a single setting entry in the settings UI. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The native base class for a single setting entry in the settings UI. This widget represents and displays a single setting definition from the <ref refid="classUSFSettingsSubsystem" kindref="compound">USFSettingsSubsystem</ref>, allowing the player to view and change the setting value. <simplesect kind="note"><para><computeroutput>Abstract</computeroutput> <computeroutput>BlueprintType</computeroutput> <computeroutput>Blueprintable</computeroutput> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
